@startuml Travel_Assistant_Activity_States
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor #E1F5FE
    BorderColor #01579B
}

[*] --> Initializing : onCreate()

Initializing --> Ready : Setup Complete

Ready --> NavigationRequested : Navigation Button Clicked
Ready --> RoutePlanningRequested : Route Planning Button Clicked
Ready --> TrafficInfoRequested : Traffic Info Button Clicked
Ready --> WeatherRequested : Weather Button Clicked
Ready --> EmergencyLocationRequested : Emergency Location Button Clicked

NavigationRequested --> Processing : Feature Coming Soon
RoutePlanningRequested --> Processing : Feature Coming Soon
TrafficInfoRequested --> Processing : Feature Coming Soon
WeatherRequested --> Processing : Feature Coming Soon

EmergencyLocationRequested --> RequestingLocation : Get GPS Location
RequestingLocation --> LocationReceived : GPS Location Obtained
RequestingLocation --> LocationError : GPS Error

LocationReceived --> SharingLocation : Share Location via SMS
SharingLocation --> LocationShared : SMS Sent
LocationShared --> Ready : Return

LocationError --> Ready : Show Error Message
Processing --> Ready : Announce Coming Soon

Ready --> Paused : onPause()
Paused --> Ready : onResume()

Ready --> [*] : onDestroy()

@enduml
